    "title_en": "Optimum spin-squeezing in Bose-Einstein condensates with particle losses",
    "abstract_en": "The problem of spin squeezing with a bimodal condensate in presence of particle losses is solved analytically by the Monte Carlo wavefunction method. We find the largest obtainable spin squeezing as a function of the one-body loss rate, the two-body and three-body rate constants, and the $s$-wave scattering length.",
